fields.value: Video and sensor data for pressure-based force calculation validation

dsDescriptionValue.value: Simultaneously-collected high speed PIV-style video of a mechanical flapping foil model of fish swimming and data from a 6-axis force-torque sensor attached to the model.  All data were collected at 1000 Hz.  PIV calibrations were set using a 2-pt method.

publicationCitation.value: Lucas KN, Dabiri JO, Lauder GV. 2017. A pressure-based force and torque prediction technique for the study of fish-like swimming. PLoS ONE 12(12): e0189225.
